---
const pageTitle = "DS-LAB | Davide Santaniello Management Engineering";
---

<html lang="it">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Code:wght@300;500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<style>
			:root {
				--primary: #284b63;
				--primary-light: #3c6e71;
				--accent: #d9d9d9;
				--bg: #ffffff;
				--text: #353535;
				--glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
			}

			* { box-sizing: border-box; }

			body {
				font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
				background-color: var(--bg);
				background-image: 
					linear-gradient(rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
					linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
				background-size: 30px 30px;
				color: var(--text);
				margin: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				padding: 2rem 1rem;
			}

			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				max-width: 1000px;
				padding: 3rem 2rem;
				background: var(--glass);
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
				border: 1px solid rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.1);
				border-radius: 24px;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
			}

			.badges {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 10px;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.badge {
				display: inline-block;
				background: var(--primary);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
				border-radius: 50px;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				font-weight: bold;
				letter-spacing: 2px;
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}

			.status-badge {
				font-size: 0.7rem;
				background: #ececec;
				color: #666;
				padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
				border-radius: 4px;
				vertical-align: middle;
				margin-left: 8px;
			}

			h1 {
				font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 5rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				color: var(--primary);
				margin: 0;
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -2px;
			}

			.subtitle {
				font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: var(--primary-light);
				margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;
			}

			.cursor {
				display: inline-block;
				width: 10px;
				height: 1.2rem;
				background-color: var(--primary-light);
				margin-left: 5px;
				animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
				vertical-align: middle;
			}

			@keyframes blink {
				from, to { opacity: 1; }
				50% { opacity: 0; }
			}

			.grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
				width: 100%;
				margin-top: 2rem;
			}

			.card {
				background: white;
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 16px;
				border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
				text-decoration: none;
				color: inherit;
				transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				text-align: left;
			}

			.card:not(.no-hover):hover {
				transform: translateY(-8px);
				border-color: var(--primary);
				box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(40, 75, 99, 0.1);
			}

			.card.full-width {
				grid-column: 1 / -1;
			}

			.card h3 {
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
				color: var(--primary);
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
			}

			.card p {
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #555;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.about-wrapper {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2.5rem;
				align-items: flex-start;
			}

			.profile-photo {
				flex-shrink: 0;
				width: 180px;
				height: 180px;
				background: #e0e0e0;
				border-radius: 20px;
				border: 4px solid white;
				box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
				overflow: hidden;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				color: #999;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 1rem;
			}

			.about-text {
				flex-grow: 1;
			}

			.about-header {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.about-name {
				font-size: 1.6rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--primary);
				margin: 0;
			}

			.about-title {
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: var(--primary-light);
				font-weight: 600;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 1px;
			}

			.about-footer {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 2rem;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}

			.social-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.social-link {
				color: var(--primary);
				font-weight: 600;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				padding: 0.5rem 0;
				border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
				transition: border-color 0.2s;
			}

			.social-link:hover {
				border-color: var(--primary);
			}

			.cv-button {
				background-color: var(--primary);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: bold;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				transition: all 0.2s;
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}

			.cv-button:hover {
				background-color: var(--primary-light);
				transform: scale(1.05);
			}

			.card-link {
				margin-top: auto;
				font-weight: bold;
				color: var(--primary);
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}

			footer {
				margin-top: 4rem;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: #999;
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.card.full-width {
					grid-column: auto;
				}
				.about-wrapper {
					flex-direction: column;
					align-items: center;
					text-align: center;
					gap: 1.5rem;
				}
				.about-footer {
					flex-direction: column;
					gap: 1.5rem;
				}
				.social-links {
					justify-content: center;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<section class="hero">
			<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
				<span class="badge" style="margin: 0;">Digital Hub</span>
				<h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 0; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1px;">DS-LAB</h1>
			</div>
			<p class="subtitle" style="margin-top: 0;">> Optimizing knowledge, engineering systems<span class="cursor"></span></p>
			
			<div class="grid">
				<!-- CARD SECOND BRAIN -->
				<a href="/notes" class="card">
					<h3>🧠 Second Brain</h3>
					<p>Il mio archivio dinamico di appunti universitari, modelli gestionali e analisi dei processi. Progettato per ottimizzare l'apprendimento strategico.</p>
					<span class="card-link">Accedi al Sistema →</span>
				</a>

				<!-- CARD MACROECONOMIA -->
				<a href="/macro" class="card">
					<h3>📈 Macro Sim <span class="status-badge" style="background: #e3f2fd; color: #1565c0; border: 1px solid #bbdefb;">Interattivo</span></h3>
					<p>Simulatori avanzati per mappare modelli economici: IS-LM, Mundell-Fleming e AD-AS. Visualizza graficamente l'impatto delle politiche fiscali e monetarie.</p>
					<span class="card-link">Accedi ai Simulatori →</span>
				</a>

				<!-- CARD PROGETTO CONSULENZA -->
				<a href="/progetto-consulenza" class="card">
					<h3>📊 Project Report</h3>
					<p>Valutazione di una proposta d'investimento analizzata sotto il profilo del posizionamento strategico e delle risorse a disposizione dell'impresa.</p>
					<span class="card-link">Visualizza Report →</span>
				</a>

				<!-- CARD PROGETTI -->
				<div class="card no-hover">
					<h3>💻 Project Lab <span class="status-badge">In Arrivo</span></h3>
					<p>Case study, analisi data-driven e modelli di ottimizzazione per la gestione aziendale. Attualmente in fase di allestimento.</p>
					<span style="color: #999; font-size: 0.9rem; font-style: italic;">Processing...</span>
				</div>

				<!-- CARD CHI SONO (FULL WIDTH) -->
				<div class="card no-hover full-width">
					<div class="about-wrapper">
						<div class="profile-photo">
							<span>Foto Profilo<br>(me.jpg)</span>
						</div>
						
						<div class="about-text">
							<div class="about-header">
								<span class="about-title">Studente di Ingegneria Gestionale</span>
								<h2 class="about-name">Davide Santaniello</h2>
							</div>
							<p>Appassionato di ottimizzazione dei processi e analisi dei dati. Mi occupo di studiare come migliorare l'efficienza dei sistemi complessi, coniugando visione strategica e competenze tecniche. Utilizzo questo spazio come laboratorio per mappare flussi di lavoro e supportare decisioni data-driven.</p>
							
							<div class="about-footer">
								<div class="social-links">
									<a href="mailto:davidesantaniello.scuola@gmail.com" class="social-link">Email</a>
									<a href="https://github.com/davide-santaniello-eng" target="_blank" class="social-link">GitHub</a>
									<a href="#" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
								</div>
								
								<a href="/cv.pdf" download class="cv-button">
									📄 Scarica CV (PDF)
								</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			&copy; 2026 Davide Santaniello — Built with Astro & Quartz
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
